<taxonomicName authority="Barták &amp; Kubík, 2018" authorityName="Barták &amp; Kubík" authorityYear="2018" box="[927,1044,295,320]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Platypalpus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="462" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bohousi" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[927,1044,295,320]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="462">P. bohousi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1052,1143,295,320]" pageId="9" pageNumber="462" rank="species">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1052,1143,295,320]" pageId="9" pageNumber="462">sp. nov.</emphasis>
</taxonomicNameLabel>
For differential diagnosis see remarks under the latter species.
</paragraph>
